casebody.data:
Tuesday, June 2, 1992

MOTION DOCKET

91- 2384. Tokles & Sons, Inc. v. Midwestern Indemn. Co.

Lucas County, No. L-89-395. On motion to dismiss, motion to strike appellant’s record and to dismiss, and motion to strike appellee’s motion for reconsideration and motion to vacate order. Motions denied.

Resnick, J., not participating.

On motion for leave to file record instanter. Motion granted.

Sweeney, Holmes and Douglas, JJ., dissent. John W. McCormac, J., of the Tenth Appellate District, sitting for Resnick, J.
